    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Queen: States if they are next to at least one ghost. Could be one ghost
    and one subject, or two subjects


    Manservant: States a character is a subject.
    Will always select ghosts if lying, or subjects if telling the truth


    Bard:
    States how far away they are from the closest ghost. If lying, states how far
    away they are from the closest subject


    Nun: States two potential subjects
    the ghost could be. One or both of the subjects could be ghosts. If lying, neither
    will be ghosts


    Knight: the second character is a ghost if and only if the
    first is a subject. If lying, the second character is a subject'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 241c6acceca8b844baad6cbcf60cefc7, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -699112959996641730, guid: 241c6acceca8b844baad6cbcf60cefc7, type: 2}
